data.title: List of Songs heard in Movies & TV Shows
data.meta_description: List of all the songs by MISSY ELLIOTT, heard in movies and tv shows. See scene descriptions, listen to their music and download songs.

Mean Girls2004

The plastics are walking down the hallway at school in slow motion. Cady falls into the trash can. Also at the end of the song is when Janis and Damin introduce Cady to the plastics.
